description:
This market will immediately resolve to “Yes” if any 1-minute candle for Penguin (PENGUIN/SOL) during Q1 2026 (from January 26 to March 31 11:59PM ET) has a final “High” price that implies a Fully Diluted Valuation (FDV) equal to or greater than the value specified in the title. Otherwise, the market will resolve to “No.”

The FDV will be calculated by multiplying the Penguin token price by the total token supply.

The resolution source for this market is Dexscreener, specifically the PENGUIN/SOL price feed available at:
https://dexscreener.com/solana/draf8qxqy86h7yehdo9gytxaf6gottt8ozjknwxv6dcs
with the chart set to “1m” (one-minute candles).

Only the Dexscreener PENGUIN/SOL price feed will be used. Prices from other exchanges, trading pairs, or data sources will not be considered.
